            <title>[DERBY-2738] Connection.isReadOnly() returns false for network client when connection is read-only due to connection level authorization.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2738</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a user has been set to read-only status using connection level authorization (e.g. is listed in derby.database.readOnlyAccessUsers) then embedded will return true for Connection.isReadOnly() but network server returns false.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
